name: Neon Babes
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:

https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi

NEON BABES

First off, I have to credit the creator of "Babes" (Alexds9) for being such an inspiration. Please do check his content, this LoRA is an homage to him. I have been very influenced by his prompting style.

Neon Babes was essentially born when I saw Alex's prompting for a babe with neon iridescent hair. I was blown away, and I knew I wanted to make this style for myself, play around with it, and eventually this LoRA was born.

I hope that you have as much fun as I did generating neon babes and that you will also take inspiration from me as I have taken inspiration from others.

Hit the dl button and let's go!
